2.a: Glory of the Fathers is a TV series starring Zhang Wanyi, Guo Tao, Liu Lin, Zhang Yue, Li Haofei, Zhou Fang, Zhang Kaitai, Li Le, Liu Pei, directed by Kang Honglei, and written by Zhao Dongling , will be broadcast on CCTV-1, Tencent Video, and Aurora TV from August 27, 2023. Based on the changes in forestry in Northeast China, the play tells a growth story about forestry reform and the realization of ecological inheritance.
